	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been using FCEUX (Win7) for awhile and like it, but I can't get it to scroll smooth (just like the original). Not sure what I'm doing wrong. I've tried a few different video settings but horizontal scrollers still &quot;jerks&quot; every now and then. I've tried both PAL and NTSC versions, no difference.<br />I've got an i5-4670 CPU running at 3.4GHz so I don't think that's the problem.<br />My screen updates at 60hz so I assume NTSC ROMs should work best but it doesn't seem to help.<br />Hints?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


