		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Smooth scrolling in NES emulators?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />FCEUX has never run perfectly smoothly for me. Things get significantly worse if there is more than once instance open (even if one is paused). You'll also notice it when something is flickering on the screen. A frame gets dropped and you get multiple consecutive &quot;on&quot; or &quot;off&quot; frames.<br /><br />I'd love to know if there's a way to improve it, but I just stick with Nestopia for playing and only use FCEUX to debug.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


