		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Smooth scrolling in NES emulators?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's never run perfectly smooth for me either, and that's under XP.  Other emulators behave fine (again on XP).  There's something about their audio/video synchronisation method, combined with the VSync option in the Video area, that causes this.<br /><br />P.S. -- When talking about these kinds of issues going forward, <strong>always</strong> disclose whether or not you're talking about in full-screen mode or in windowed mode.  <strong>Yes it matters</strong>.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


